  "description": "Open-ecos icsprout55 55nm PDK (non-Ciel, on-disk). Materialized: tech-LEF + std-cell (RVT/HVT/LVT, H7C) LEF/GDS/Verilog + 7-corner NLDM Liberty (tt/ss/ff with cworst/rcworst/cbest/rcbest RC variants) + IO LEF/GDS/Liberty -> place + STA-signoff-able. Large .lib/.gds are release assets fetched by `make unzip` into $ICSPROUT55_PDK (git mirror carries LEF/CDL/Verilog + the fetch mechanism). Not yet upstream: SPICE/RC models + DRC/LVS decks, so extraction/DRC/LVS remain gated. Mirrored under github.com/vyges-tools."
